description:
Sometimes you just have to take a stand. For those occasions, Feedback Sports tailored this heavy-duty padded tote to fit their Pro-Elite, Classic, Sport and similarly sized bike stands.

  • Made of padded nylon to protect the stand when not in use
  • Full-length zipper for easy access
  • 2 carrying straps distribute weight for comfortable portage
  • Dimensions are 122 x 15 x 15cm
name: Feedback Sports Tote for Elite, Classic  & Sport Workstand
